rows.label: qev060403_MSG0003
rows.name: A-aaah... Urrgh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0001
rows.name:
*fsssh* Phew. That was a devoltanization that touched
the very core of my soul.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0002
rows.name:
Hmm? Who are you? *fsssh*
And what are you doing in such a place as this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_JNK0010
rows.name: Explain

rows.label: qev060403_SEL0011
rows.name: Fill Arsenican in on the situation.

rows.label: qev060403_JNK0020
rows.name: Sigh

rows.label: qev060403_SEL0021
rows.name: Heave a mighty sigh at Arsenican's obliviousness.

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0009
rows.name:
You came here to protect me at Trachlo Lythren's
request? *fsssh* Interesting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0012
rows.name: ...WHAT?! I was attacked by an indigen?! *fssssssssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0010
rows.name:
I am terribly sorry. *fsssh* During the devoltanizing
process, my focus is so narrow that I frequently lose
sight of my surroundings.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0011
rows.name:
*fsssh* Thank you for the very thorough explanation.
I now understand that I owe you my life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0014
rows.name:
*fsssh* Well, of course I cannot move during the
devoltanization process.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0015
rows.name: ...WHAT?! I was attacked by an indigen?! *fssssssssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0016
rows.name:
And you saved me... *fsssh*
I was completely unaware.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0017
rows.name:
You are right to be exasperated with me. *fsssh*
I offer my sincere apologies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0020
rows.name:
Thank you. *fsssh*
I will return to New LA at once.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0021
rows.name:
I have caused some trouble for my people. *fsssh*
Perhaps I will pick them some poisonous mushrooms
on the way back as recompense.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0022
rows.name:
Nngh... My soul feels so desiccated. *fsssh*
I must devoltanize the impurities of this world.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0023
rows.name:
...N-no! *fsssh* Must stay strong... Though as soon as
I let my guard down, I feel myself ready to wander...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0024
rows.name:
Arsenican! *fsssh* Golbogga did not grant you life so
that you might cavalierly risk it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0025
rows.name:
Y-yes, of course. *fsssh* I will restrict myself to what
voltant I can find within the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060403_MSG0026
rows.name:
And yet... The voltant of the planet calls me to...
No! Stay strong! M-must stay strong! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]
